&lt;p&gt;The "problem" is that &lt;code&gt;{{range}}&lt;/code&gt; changes the pipeline (the &lt;em&gt;dot&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;code&gt;.&lt;/code&gt;) to the current item, so inside the &lt;code&gt;{{range}}&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

